Delayed::AsynchMailer
==========

This enables asynchronus mail delivery.
To achieve it you need to include Delayed::AsynchMailer module in your mailers.
Calls to Mailer.deliver_some_email will be asynchronous.
To send an email synchrounsly call Mailer.deliver_some_email!

Example
=======

class SomeMailer < ActionMailer::Base
  include Delayed::AsynchMailer

  def test_mail
    ...
  end
end

SomeMailer.deliver_test_mail  # Asynchronus call
SomeMailer.deliver_test_mail! # Synchronus call

